description:
The Dose Response Module extends LabChart to provide dose response curves and analysis from recorded LabChart data. The results can also be exported to applications, such as GraphPad Prism, if required.


Changes Since Previous Version
There have been various enhancements and changes to the following:
- The Dose Response Tutorial file has been updated
- The Dose Response online help has been updated with information about valid <dose> and <drug-name> formats for Dose Response Comments.
Known Issues
- Dose Response files exported as XML open correctly under Prism 5 but display an error message under Prism 6. The error message can however be ignored, as the file is read correctly
